SVGSymbolElement.summary: The SVGSymbolElement interface corresponds to the symbol element.

SVGSymbolElementPreserveAspectRatio.summary: The preserveAspectRatio read-only property of the interface reflects the {{SVGAttr("preserveAspectRatio")}} attribute of the given {{SVGElement("symbol")}} element. It defines how the symbol's content should be scaled to fit the given space, preserving its aspect ratio.

SVGSymbolElementViewBox.summary: The viewBox read-only property of the interface reflects the {{SVGAttr("viewBox")}} attribute of the given {{SVGElement("symbol")}} element.
